org.eclipse.dataset

Class SliceNDIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.dataset.IndexIterator
      • org.eclipse.dataset.SliceNDIterator

  • public class SliceNDIterator
extends IndexIterator

    Class to provide slice iteration through a dataset

    It allows a number of axes to be omitted and iterates over the axes left over.
